      {
        "block_label": "text",
        "block_content": "details in Table 3. The results show that both DP-SGD and RandAugment effectively defend against LSA as well as our GSA $ _{1} $ and GSA $ _{2} $, reducing the attack ASR and AUC to levels similar to random guessing. The defense effects are also visualized in Figure 7.",
